# Environment Variables

## Required Variables

### Database
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://your-connection-string
MONGO_URI_DEV=mongodb://localhost:27017/mycircle

### Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-min-32-characters
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret
GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID=your-android-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_IOS_CLIENT_ID=your-ios-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com

### Cloudinary (Image Upload)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your-cloud-name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your-api-key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your-api-secret

## Optional Variables

### AI Features (Gemini)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key

### Application
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
CLIENT_URL_DEV=http://localhost:5173

# Comma-separated origins allowed in production CORS/Socket.io (example)
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://yourdomain.com,https://www.yourdomain.com
CORS_ORIGINS=

## Notes

- Never commit the actual .env file to version control
- Use strong, unique values for JWT_SECRET (minimum 32 characters)
- Get Google OAuth credentials from https://console.cloud.google.com
- Get Cloudinary credentials from https://cloudinary.com
- Get Gemini API key from https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
